long_desc.thetext:
Tracker for async updates of golang-github-aws-aws-sdk-go for rawhide and other fedora distribution.
As golang devel packages are used only as a build-time dependency at the moment, this tracker keeps updates and other information about this package, e.g. broken dependencies, exceptions, important pieces of information and other issues.
golang-github-aws-aws-sdk-go-0.9.5-1.el6 has been submitted as an update to Fedora EPEL 6. https://bodhi.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-EPEL-2015-7e24cd3d92

golang-github-aws-aws-sdk-go-0.9.5-1.fc23 has been pushed to the Fedora 23 testing repository. If problems still persist, please make note of it in this bug report. If you want to test the update, you can install it with $ su -c 'dnf --enablerepo=updates-testing update golang-github-aws-aws-sdk-go' You can provide feedback for this update here: https://bodhi.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-2015-14b327234c
